@0xb35c ... one last try: can you check with `type=simple`?

We didn't imagine `play kube` to be used in a systemd unit. With v2.0, `podman generate systemd` supports the `--new` flag also for pods, which may be something more reliable for your use case. However, v1.6.4 is too old to properly support these new features.

It looks like `oneshot` is shooting down the containers.
